<span id="freeTextContainer7887799418779296048">It&apos;s been a while since I&apos;ve read one of Peters&apos; Cadfael books. It took the prompting of a GR friend to get me back at it, and I&apos;m glad I did! These are fun, at least for historical fiction lovers who also like a bit of detective fiction. In this one all kinds of folks are dying and getting kidnapped. Moves quickly. Good entertainment!</span>
  <span id="freeText7887799418779296048" style="display:none">It's been a while since I've read one of Peters' Cadfael books. It took the prompting of a GR friend to get me back at it, and I'm glad I did! These are fun, at least for historical fiction lovers who also like a bit of detective fiction. In this one all kinds of folks are dying and getting kidnapped. Moves quickly. Good entertainment!</span>
