<span id="freeTextContainer16996583326006327439">This series is so comforting to me. Given my current level of rage over the forced-birthers passing laws to turn women into breeding machines, hanging out with Brother Cadfael in 11th Century Wales is basically a great choice.<br/><br/>Brother Cadfael respected women. It&apos;s really sad when I have to turn to a fictitious 11th century monk for comfort.</span>
  <span id="freeText16996583326006327439" style="display:none">This series is so comforting to me. Given my current level of rage over the forced-birthers passing laws to turn women into breeding machines, hanging out with Brother Cadfael in 11th Century Wales is basically a great choice.<br /><br />Brother Cadfael respected women. It's really sad when I have to turn to a fictitious 11th century monk for comfort.</span>
