        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer17800504" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16297978810622656803">Runaway Villeins, tyranical masters, disappeared novices, young lordling being foced to marry. A murdered courier an empress under siege. This Cadfael story had all the best elements of the series and brought new twists to boring old life in the 12th century. <br/><br/>This one never made it to TV, not sure why but it&apos;s vintage Cadfael. An enjoyable read that&apos;s actually a bit more of a mystery than most. </span>
  <span id="freeText16297978810622656803" style="display:none">Runaway Villeins, tyranical masters, disappeared novices, young lordling being foced to marry. A murdered courier an empress under siege. This Cadfael story had all the best elements of the series and brought new twists to boring old life in the 12th century. <br /><br />This one never made it to TV, not sure why but it's vintage Cadfael. An enjoyable read that's actually a bit more of a mystery than most. </span>
